'''愛彼'''（英文：'''Audemars Piguet'''），是[[瑞士|瑞士]]頂級钟表品牌、制造商，总部位于[[瑞士|瑞士]]布拉苏斯（Le Brassus）。<ref name=":7">{{Cite web|url=https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/origins|title=Audemars Piguet {{!}} Our origins|language=en|website=Audemars Piguet - Le Brassus|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216120912/https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/origins/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 公司1875年由朱尔斯·路易斯·奥德莫斯（Jules Louis Audemars）和爱德华·奥古斯蒂·皮捷特（Edward Auguste Piguet）在瑞士的[[汝拉山谷|汝拉山谷]]建立，并一直保持家族式经营。<ref name=":72">{{Cite web|url=https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/origins|title=Audemars Piguet {{!}} Our origins|language=en|website=Audemars Piguet - Le Brassus|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216120912/https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/origins/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":5">{{Cite web|url=https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/independence|title=Audemars Piguet {{!}} Spirit of Independence|language=en|website=Audemars Piguet - Le Brassus|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216164020/https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/independence/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

爱彼是世界上最著名的高端钟表品牌之一。<ref name=":9">{{Cite web|url=https://www.luxos.com/news/watches/2738-timeless-audemars-piguet-have-a-world-leading-reputation-for-their-exclusive-timepieces|title=Timeless: Audemars Piguet have a world-leading reputation for their exclusive timepieces|language=en-gb|website=www.luxos.com|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216074323/https://www.luxos.com/news/watches/2738-timeless-audemars-piguet-have-a-world-leading-reputation-for-their-exclusive-timepieces|archive-date=2018-12-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=":142">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/history/h/audemars-piguet/|title=Audemars Piguet History - Fondation de la Haute Horlogerie|last=|first=|date=|website=www.hautehorlogerie.org|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190104133614/https://www.hautehorlogerie.org/en/brands/history/h/audemars-piguet/|archive-date=2019-01-04|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-02-02}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=https://blog.crownandcaliber.com/the-history-of-audemars-piguet/|title=The History of Audemars Piguet|date=2018-07-18|language=en-US|website=Crown & Caliber Blog|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216163358/https://blog.crownandcaliber.com/the-history-of-audemars-piguet/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/why-isnt-rolex-considered-one-of-the-big-three|title=Letters To The Editor: Why Isn't Rolex Considered One Of 'The Big Three'?|last=July 7|first=Jack Forster|language=en|last2=2017|website=HODINKEE|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216074141/https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/why-isnt-rolex-considered-one-of-the-big-three|dead-url=no}}</ref> 该品牌依靠1972年推出的“皇家橡树（Royal Oak）”系列腕表在钟表界脱颖而出。<ref name=":4" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hauteliving.com/2012/08/the-saga-of-steel/305399/|title=The Saga of Steel: The Audemars Piguet Royal Oak|date=2012-08-07|last=Forster|first=Jack|language=en-US|website=Haute Living|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2020-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200319035412/https://hauteliving.com/2012/08/the-saga-of-steel/305399/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":6">{{Cite web|url=https://swissdiverswatches.com/audemars-piguet-brand-review|title=Audemars Piguet brand review {{!}} Swiss Divers Watches|language=en-US|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216120717/https://swissdiverswatches.com/audemars-piguet-brand-review|dead-url=no}}</ref> 1892年，爱彼制造出了世界上第一款[[语音报时|三问报时]]腕表的机芯，并于1934年推出了世界第一款镂空怀表，还制造出过世界上许多最薄的表款。<ref name=":142" /><ref name=":3" /><ref name=":16">{{Cite web|url=https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/innovation|title=Audemars Piguet {{!}} Innovation: Tradition & Avant-garde|website=Audemars Piguet - Le Brassus|language=en|access-date=2019-02-03|archive-date=2019-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190204070013/https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/innovation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==历史==

=== 早期历史 ===
朱尔斯·路易斯·奥德莫斯（Jules Louis Audemars）和爱德华·奥古斯蒂·皮捷特（Edward Auguste Piguet）从小便相识，但直到1874年两人20岁出头时才重新熟络起来。<ref name=":32">{{Cite web|url=https://blog.crownandcaliber.com/the-history-of-audemars-piguet/|title=The History of Audemars Piguet|date=2018-07-18|language=en-US|website=Crown & Caliber Blog|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216163358/https://blog.crownandcaliber.com/the-history-of-audemars-piguet/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 1875年， 23岁的朱尔斯和21岁的爱德华决定开设一家制表作坊，取两人的名字作为品牌名称，也就是''爱彼（Audemars Piguet''）。<ref name=":32" /><ref name=":82">{{Cite web|url=https://uk.bucherer.com/editorial/audemars-piguet-a-brand-history/|title=Audemars Piguet: A Brand History {{!}} Editorial {{!}} Bucherer|date=2013-03-04|language=en-US|website=Editorial|access-date=2018-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221041326/https://uk.bucherer.com/editorial/audemars-piguet-a-brand-history/|archive-date=2018-12-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Glass">{{cite journal|author=Cat Tsang|issue=6|title=Markers of Time|journal=[http://www.glassmagazine.co.uk/ Glass Magazine]|pages=72–74|location=London|issn=2041-6318|date=June 2011}}</ref> 公司选址在布拉苏斯（Le Brassus），是瑞士[[汝拉山谷|汝拉山谷]]中的一个小镇。<ref name=":73">{{Cite web|url=https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/origins|title=Audemars Piguet {{!}} Our origins|language=en|website=Audemars Piguet - Le Brassus|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216120912/https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/origins/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[File:Audemars_2385_00.jpg|缩略图]]朱尔斯和爱德华均为制表人。朱尔斯擅长制作复杂机芯，而爱德华擅长机芯调整和管理。二人分工明确、配合默契，公司成立后朱尔斯负责技术生产，爱德华负责销售和公司运营。<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=https://www.govbergwatches.com/blog/a-brief-history-of-audemars-piguet/#|title=A History of Audemars Piguet {{!}} AP Watches|date=2015-06-15|work=Govberg Jewelers|language=en-US|access-date=2017-10-04|archive-date=2017-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171005051302/https://www.govbergwatches.com/blog/a-brief-history-of-audemars-piguet/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bucherer.co.uk/editorial/audemars-piguet-a-brand-history/|title=Audemars Piguet: A Brand History {{!}} Editorial {{!}} The Watch Gallery|date=2013-03-04|work=Editorial|language=en-US|access-date=2017-10-04}}{{Dead link|date=2020年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

从1882年开始，愛彼家族始终没有放弃其家族在董事会的股权。第二代传人包括Paul Louis Audemars 和 Paul Edward Piguet, 而第三代传人包括Jacques Louis Audemars 和 Paulette Piguet。<ref name=":52">{{Cite web|url=https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/independence|title=Audemars Piguet {{!}} Spirit of Independence|language=en|website=Audemars Piguet - Le Brassus|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216164020/https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/independence/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 近期发展 ===
1970年代，[[石英危机|石英危机]]（quartz crisis）期间，爱彼在世界制表业中地位逐渐上升，特别是在推出皇家橡树系列腕表之后。<ref name=":33">{{Cite web|url=https://blog.crownandcaliber.com/the-history-of-audemars-piguet/|title=The History of Audemars Piguet|date=2018-07-18|language=en-US|website=Crown & Caliber Blog|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216163358/https://blog.crownandcaliber.com/the-history-of-audemars-piguet/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":62">{{Cite web|url=https://swissdiverswatches.com/audemars-piguet-brand-review|title=Audemars Piguet brand review {{!}} Swiss Divers Watches|language=en-US|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216120717/https://swissdiverswatches.com/audemars-piguet-brand-review|dead-url=no}}</ref> 截止至2018年，公司现由爱彼家族的第四代传人经营，包括 Jasmine Audemars 和 Olivier Frank Edward Audemars。<ref name=":53">{{Cite web|url=https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/independence|title=Audemars Piguet {{!}} Spirit of Independence|language=en|website=Audemars Piguet - Le Brassus|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216164020/https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/independence/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

爱彼是瑞士钟表业协会（Federation of the Swiss Watch Industry）的主要会员。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fhs.swiss/eng/watch_brands.html?letter=A|title=Our brands|date=|last=|first=|website=Federation of the Swiss watch industry|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181218054542/https://www.fhs.swiss/eng/watch_brands.html?letter=A|archive-date=2018-12-18|dead-url=no|access-date=}}</ref>

