=== 重要发明及专利 ===

* 1892年，爱彼制造出了世界上第一款[[语音报时|三问报时]]腕表的机芯、并卖给了[[歐米茄_(公司)|欧米伽公司]]，使得后者的创始人Louis Brandt成功制造出了世界上第一款三问报时腕表。<ref name=":16" /><ref name=":17">{{Cite web|url=https://www.watchtime.com/featured/7-milestone-omega-watches-from-1892-to-today/|title=7 Milestone Omega Watches, from 1892 to Today|last=Brunner|first=Written byGisbert|date=2018-07-12|website=WatchTime - USA's No.1 Watch Magazine|language=en-US|access-date=2019-02-03|archive-date=2019-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190204014329/https://www.watchtime.com/featured/7-milestone-omega-watches-from-1892-to-today/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.timewerke.com/?p=3243|title=The world’s first wristwatch minute repeater: Still sound {{!}} TIMEWERKE|last=Tan|first=Timmy|language=en-US|access-date=2019-02-03|archive-date=2020-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200808085940/https://www.timewerke.com/?p=3243|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*1899年，制造出了超复杂怀表（Grand Complication）、拥有7项复杂功能，包括三问报时、闹钟、万年历、计时功能等。<ref name=":35">{{Cite web|url=https://blog.crownandcaliber.com/the-history-of-audemars-piguet/|title=The History of Audemars Piguet|date=2018-07-18|website=Crown & Caliber Blog|language=en-US|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216163358/https://blog.crownandcaliber.com/the-history-of-audemars-piguet/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*1921年，推出了世界第一款跳时腕表（jumping-hour）。<ref name=":35" /><ref name=":84">{{Cite web|url=https://uk.bucherer.com/editorial/audemars-piguet-a-brand-history/|title=Audemars Piguet: A Brand History {{!}} Editorial {{!}} Bucherer|date=2013-03-04|website=Editorial|language=en-US|access-date=2018-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221041326/https://uk.bucherer.com/editorial/audemars-piguet-a-brand-history/|archive-date=2018-12-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
* 1934年，推出了世界第一款镂空表。<ref name=":84" />
* 1946年，制造出世界上最薄手表。<ref name=":84" />
* 1972年，推出了世界第一款豪华运动手表——皇家橡树。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://journal.hautehorlogerie.org/en/the-royal-oak-design-revolution/|title=The Royal Oak design revolution – FHH Journal|website=journal.hautehorlogerie.org|language=en-US|access-date=2019-01-19|archive-date=2019-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190120093440/https://journal.hautehorlogerie.org/en/the-royal-oak-design-revolution/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 环保评级 ===
2018年12月，[[世界自然基金会|世界自然基金会]]（WWF）发布官方报告，包含对瑞士15个主要钟表及珠宝生产商的环保评级。<ref name=":442">{{Cite web|url=https://www.wwf.ch/sites/default/files/doc-2018-12/2018_12_07_WWF%20Watch%20and%20Jewellery%20Report%202018_final_e_0.pdf|title=Environmental rating and industry report 2018|last=|first=|date=|website=World Wide Fund for Nature|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190120043234/https://www.wwf.ch/sites/default/files/doc-2018-12/2018_12_07_WWF%20Watch%20and%20Jewellery%20Report%202018_final_e_0.pdf|archive-date=2019-01-20|dead-url=no|access-date=2019-01-19}}</ref><ref name=":452">{{Cite web|url=https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/politics/benchmark-report_swiss-luxury-watches-fail-to-meet-environmental-standards/44628536|title=Swiss luxury watches fail to meet environmental standards|last=swissinfo.ch|first=S. W. I.|last2=Corporation|first2=a branch of the Swiss Broadcasting|website=SWI swissinfo.ch|language=en|access-date=2019-01-19|archive-date=2019-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190120043225/https://www.swissinfo.ch/eng/politics/benchmark-report_swiss-luxury-watches-fail-to-meet-environmental-standards/44628536|dead-url=no}}</ref> 其中爱彼连同其它7个生产商（包括[[百达翡丽|百达翡丽]]、[[寶璣|宝玑]]、[[劳力士|劳力士]]）的评级为最低档（"Latecomers/Non-transparent"），意味着作为钟表生产商爱彼仅采取了非常有限的措施以消除其生产活动对环境及气候变化所造成的影响。<ref name=":442" />

主要的环保隐患有二：1）生产活动的不透明；2）对珍贵原材料的大量开采，主要包括[[金|金矿]]。而后者是造成众多环境问题的重要因素之一，比如水土污染、土壤退化、森林破坏等。<ref name=":442" /><ref name=":452" /> 据估计，钟表及珠宝行业每年消耗超过2000吨的黄金，占全球黄金产量的50%以上，而大多数情况下，钟表制造公司不能或不愿意说明其原材料的来源以及原材料供应商是否采用环保的开采方式。<ref name=":442" />

