=== 皇家橡树 ===
皇家橡树（Royal Oak）系列腕表被誉为爱彼最受欢迎的旗舰产品。<ref name=":92">{{Cite web|url=https://www.luxos.com/news/watches/2738-timeless-audemars-piguet-have-a-world-leading-reputation-for-their-exclusive-timepieces|title=Timeless: Audemars Piguet have a world-leading reputation for their exclusive timepieces|language=en-gb|website=www.luxos.com|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216074323/https://www.luxos.com/news/watches/2738-timeless-audemars-piguet-have-a-world-leading-reputation-for-their-exclusive-timepieces|archive-date=2018-12-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=":34">{{Cite web|url=https://blog.crownandcaliber.com/the-history-of-audemars-piguet/|title=The History of Audemars Piguet|date=2018-07-18|language=en-US|website=Crown & Caliber Blog|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216163358/https://blog.crownandcaliber.com/the-history-of-audemars-piguet/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":42">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/why-isnt-rolex-considered-one-of-the-big-three|title=Letters To The Editor: Why Isn't Rolex Considered One Of 'The Big Three'?|last=July 7|first=Jack Forster|language=en|last2=2017|website=HODINKEE|access-date=2018-12-16|archive-date=2018-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181216074141/https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/why-isnt-rolex-considered-one-of-the-big-three|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":83">{{Cite web|url=https://uk.bucherer.com/editorial/audemars-piguet-a-brand-history/|title=Audemars Piguet: A Brand History {{!}} Editorial {{!}} Bucherer|date=2013-03-04|language=en-US|website=Editorial|access-date=2018-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221041326/https://uk.bucherer.com/editorial/audemars-piguet-a-brand-history/|archive-date=2018-12-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 皇家橡树腕表最初由瑞士制表师杰罗·尊达（Gérald Genta）设计，[[石英危机|石英危机]]期间，爱彼在1972年的巴塞尔钟表展（Baseworld）上推出该系列。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/legacy/unleashing-the-beast|title=Audemars Piguet {{!}} Unleashing the Beast|accessdate=2019-01-06|work=Audemars Piguet - Le Brassus|language=en|archive-date=2018-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181103091946/https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/made-in-le-brassus/legacy/unleashing-the-beast/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.govbergwatches.com/blog/audemars-piguet-royal-oak-history/|title=Audemars Piguet Royal Oak 45th Anniversary {{!}} History of the Royal Oak|date=2017-05-31|work=Govberg Jewelers|language=en-US|access-date=2017-10-04|archive-date=2017-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171005051957/https://www.govbergwatches.com/blog/audemars-piguet-royal-oak-history/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 而为了纪念皇家橡树推出20年，爱彼于1993年推出了皇家橡树离岸（Royal Oak Offshore）系列腕表。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/new/royal-oak-25-years|title=Audemars Piguet {{!}} The Royal Oak Offshore Celebrates 25 Years|language=en|website=Audemars Piguet - Le Brassus|access-date=2018-12-19|archive-date=2018-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221041533/https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/new/royal-oak-25-years/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.timeandwatches.com/p/history-of-audemars-piguet-royal-oak.html|title=History of the Audemars Piguet Royal Oak|website=Time and Watches|access-date=2017-10-04|archive-date=2017-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171014115642/http://www.timeandwatches.com/p/history-of-audemars-piguet-royal-oak.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 千禧系列 ===
爱彼于1995年推出千禧系列手表（Millenary collection）。表款的特点是让佩戴者能三维立体地观察到手表内部机芯。<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/watch-collection/millenary/|title=Audemars Piguet - Swiss Luxury Watches|language=en|website=Audemars Piguet - Le Brassus|access-date=2017-10-06|archive-date=2017-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171006212120/https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/watch-collection/millenary/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

