该表款以创始人朱尔斯·路易斯·奥德莫斯（Jules Louis Audemars）名字命名，采用较为传统的设计理念，均采用圆形表壳设计。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/watch-collection/jules-audemars/|title=Jules Audemars|date=|last=|first=|website=Audemars Piguet - Le Brassus|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171013224855/https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/watch-collection/jules-audemars/|archive-date=2017-10-13|dead-url=no|access-date=2017-10-13}}</ref><ref name=":22">{{Cite web|url=https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/watch-collection/millenary/|title=Audemars Piguet - Swiss Luxury Watches|language=en|website=Audemars Piguet - Le Brassus|access-date=2017-10-06|archive-date=2017-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171006212120/https://www.audemarspiguet.com/en/watch-collection/millenary/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

